{"tid":1325782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"7·21 一齊代梁天琦走下去","createTime":"2019-07-17T03:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T20:16:46.000Z","uid":92836,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b1712f50d6a8f25e8335c98a37f41170576024a9","tid":1325782,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:49:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">時代革命、光復香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9qx0mKp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qx0mKp.jpg&h=e9fe95b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n回憶下大家一路以黎嘅努力<br />\n好攰但真係要繼續走下去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">等我為大家回憶下決定721去定唔去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></div><br />\n<br />\n制度暴力投訴無門<br />\n所以先要走上街頭<br />\n抛頭髗、灑熱血<br />\n<br />\n人民唔應該害怕政府、政府應該害怕人民<br />\n因為主權在民<br />\n我地香港人先香港呢片土地嘅主人<br />\n<br />\n屋企嘅將來大家一齊創建"},{"pid":"722bf0c87ced3221753e30cb405a097c192f7085","tid":1325782,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:07:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">721金鐘見！</span>"},{"pid":"830d450829af2c2a6baf281162687ba2c54e5ec8","tid":1325782,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:07:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">721金鐘見！</span>"},{"pid":"0e9727280ebaa30d478915de61b1f482478056ab","tid":1325782,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:07:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">721金鐘見！</span>"},{"pid":"efaed13d2ab6c83f0c9c78acc8bda3d290f946db","tid":1325782,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">721金鐘見！</span>"},{"pid":"e8f773b590a35c1a813aeb3277f30f135b886642","